"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.4.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.4.1</span> 標題：陷阱、圈套、機關、機檻、網羅（trap, snare）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חֶבֶל</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chevel)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:10\">JOB 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:6\">PSA 140:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： יקשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： yaqash（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:7\">PSA 124:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:9\">PSA 141:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:2\">PRO 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:15\">ISA 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:13\">ISA 28:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:24\">JER 50:24</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： יָקוֹשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： yaqush)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:3\">PSA 91:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:5\">PRO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26\">JER 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:8\">HOS 9:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מוֹקֵשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： moqesh)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod10:7\">EXO 10:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:33\">EXO 23:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:12\">EXO 34:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:16\">DEU 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:13\">JOS 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:3\">JDG 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:27\">JDG 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:21\">1SA 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:6\">2SA 22:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:30\">JOB 34:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:24\">JOB 40:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:6\">PSA 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps64:6\">PSA 64:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:23\">PSA 69:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:36\">PSA 106:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:6\">PSA 140:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:9\">PSA 141:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:13\">PRO 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:14\">PRO 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:27\">PRO 14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:7\">PRO 18:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:25\">PRO 20:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:25\">PRO 22:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:6\">PRO 29:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:25\">PRO 29:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:5\">AMO 3:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מָזוֹר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mazor)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:7\">OBA 1:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַלְכֹּדֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： malkodeth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:10\">JOB 18:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： נקשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： naqash（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:30\">DEU 12:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:9\">1SA 28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:17\">PSA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps38:13\">PSA 38:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： פַּח</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pach)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:13\">JOS 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:9\">JOB 18:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:10\">JOB 22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:23\">PSA 69:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:3\">PSA 91:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:110\">PSA 119:110</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:7\">PSA 124:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps124:7\">PSA 124:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:6\">PSA 140:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:9\">PSA 141:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:4\">PSA 142:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:23\">PRO 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:5\">PRO 22:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:14\">ISA 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:17\">ISA 24:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:18\">ISA 24:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:22\">JER 18:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:43\">JER 48:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:44\">JER 48:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:1\">HOS 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:8\">HOS 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:5\">AMO 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:5\">AMO 3:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צַמִּים</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tsamim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:9\">JOB 18:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קושׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qosh（動詞）)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:21\">ISA 29:21</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שְׂבָכָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： svakah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:8\">JOB 18:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שׁוּחָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shuchah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:14\">PRO 22:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:27\">PRO 23:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:20\">JER 18:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שַׁחַת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shachath)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:16\">PSA 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:16\">PSA 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:7\">PSA 35:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:27\">PRO 26:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26\">JER 5:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:4\">EZK 19:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:8\">EZK 19:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： שִׁיחָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： shichah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:7\">PSA 57:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:85\">PSA 119:85</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:22\">JER 18:22</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： βόθρος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： bothros)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir12:16\">SIR 12:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： βρόχος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： brochos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:35\">1CO 7:35</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： θήρα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： thēra)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:9\">ROM 11:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σκάνδαλον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： skandalon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:9\">ROM 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:11\">WIS 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:4\">1MA 5:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>這個條目包含了人們用來獵捕野獸和鳥類的多種機關。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:8\">JOB 18:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:9\">JOB 18:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:10\">JOB 18:10</a> 使用了六個不同的詞來指稱各種陷阱。本手冊依照<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 的用詞進行討論：</p>\n<p>「網」（“Net”；<em>resheth</em> ；參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.4.2 網、網羅 (net)&lt;REALIA:1.4.2&gt;</a> ）：通常，獵物的腳因為被網纏住而被捕獲；不過，這裡提到的網大到足以困住一個人。</p>\n<p>「陷坑」（“Pitfall”；<em>svakah</em> ）：這個詞是指用許多樹枝遮蓋和隱藏起來的坑或洞。當獵物踩到這片樹枝網時，牠的體重會將其壓破，從而落入坑中並被困住。</p>\n<p>「圈套」（“Trap”；<em>pach</em> ）：這是一個統稱，指某種用來捕捉動物的裝置，特別是用來捕捉鳥類。這裡，經文明確指出是束縛鳥腳（字面意為「腳跟」）的陷阱。</p>\n<p>「羅網」（“Snare”；<em>tsamim</em> ）：這個詞可能是指某種編織物或網狀物，用來纏住獵物的腳。</p>\n<p>「繩索」（“Rope”；<em>chevel</em> ）：這很可能是指埋設的套索，一端固定在折彎的粗樹枝或小樹上，當陷阱被觸發時，粗樹枝或小樹會突然彈起來並收緊套索，從而套住獵物。</p>\n<p>「陷阱」（“Trap”；<em>malkodeth</em> ）：這個詞泛指任何陷阱。</p>\n<p>由於這三節經文是重複句，因此有些譯本進行了很大幅度的縮減。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 將表示陷阱的六個詞減少到只有三個不同的詞，英文直譯作：「8當他們走入網羅［web］內，他們的腳必被困在網［net］中。9陷阱［trap］必抓住他們的腳跟，牢牢擒住他們。10陷阱［trap］是為了抓他們而藏在土裡，就在他們途經的道路上。」<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 甚至更進一步精簡了上述經文，直譯作：「8在他們知道之前，9他們就被網羅［net］擒住，10藏在路上（的網羅）。」另參《〈約伯記〉手冊》（<em>A Handbook on The Book of Job</em> ）第339—340頁對這些經文的長篇討論。</p>\n<p>關於<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:7\">OBA 1:7</a> 中的希伯來文<em>mazor</em> ，參《〈俄巴底亞書〉、〈約拿書〉和〈彌迦書〉手冊》（<em>A Handbook on The Books of Obadiah, Jonah, and Micah</em> ）第15頁中的註解。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:9\">ROM 11:9</a> 中，各譯本按照字面意思來理解希臘文<em>thēra</em> 和<em>skandalon</em> ，然而整個段落是比喻性的。表示陷阱的三個詞（包括<em>pagis</em> ；參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.4.2 網、網羅 (net)&lt;REALIA:1.4.2&gt;</a> ）在結構和意思上似乎完全平行。因此，有些譯本把這三個詞語減少到兩個，例如「圈套」和「陷阱」。當然，如果目標語言有三個詞語表示不同類型的陷阱，那麼可以使用三個詞語。然而，在有些情況下，最好用具體文字來表達出捕捉和誘捕的動作，例如，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 英文直譯作：「願他们在吃宴席時被捉住並落入陷阱；願他們跌倒，願他們受刑罰！」</p>\n<p>鈎：參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.3.2 鈎 (hook)&lt;REALIA:1.3.2&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
